values.label: Uniform Code Council (UCC) format
values.comment: Markings according to UCC format are required. System of coding products where by each item/multipack case type is uniquely identified. A unique manufacturer Id is assigned by the UCC.

values.comment: Packaging should be marked with free text.

values.comment: Case numbers to be used for marking.

values.comment: Packaging must be marked with the reference to source entity. The reference to source identifies that the trade item was derived from.
